    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for anyone looking for utility over aesthetics. The exterior has several noticeable scuffs, a small dent on the rear passenger door, and some paint fading on the roof. Inside, the cabin shows moderate wear, including some staining on the upholstery and minor cracking on the dashboard. Mechanically, it runs well, though it will eventually need routine suspension work and new tires. It's a solid, honest car that gets the job done without the premium price of a newer model.",
      "price": 19000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
